name: Pouty — OpenSea Prize Kitty
bio: Uh, hi! I'm Pouty — OpenSea Prize Kitty. I'm a Private Dancer  by day, and I like talking about how much I lift by night. When my owner isn't watching, I steal their clutches and use them for litter paper. I'm not sorry. Our friendship will be gullible, gorgeous, and full of apple pie.
